edu.utexas.cs.tamerProject.params
Class Params

java.lang.Object
  edu.utexas.cs.tamerProject.params.Params

public class Params
extends java.lang.Object

Params is where the parameters are set that are specific to an agent type, an agent's approach to an environment (e.g., representation of Q or H), experimental conditions, and anything else that calls for changes in the agent algorithm.
